Minecraft can be played using on your chromebook with this link:
https://ubg100.github.io/eaglercraft.html

If the link above are banned, you can find them on other websites (such as the ones in this folder and the Hubs folder).
By the way, the version linked above is Java. You can find Bedrock though on other websites, as mentioned above.

